criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  DM1;

          -  Use of insulin pump;

          -  Disease duration ≥ 3 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence of chronic complications of DM (including cardiovascular autonomic
             neuropathy);

          -  BMI ≥ 30 kg/m2;

          -  Presence of chronic diseases other than DM1;

          -  Diseases that interfere with GE;

          -  Medications that interfere with blood glucose homeostasis (except insulin) and GE.
